[ti:Everything Goes On (群星依旧)][ar:Porter Robinson,英雄联盟][al:Everything Goes On (群星依旧)][offset:0][from:https://lrc.64h.cn][length:[03:19.00]][00:00.00]Everything Goes On (群星依旧) - Porter Robinson/英雄联盟[00:06.00]Lyrics by：Porter Robinson[00:07.00]Composed by：Porter Robinson/Brendon Williams (拳头游戏) /Fredrik Johansson/Hige Driver[00:15.00]Don't try to make yourself remember darling[00:21.00]Don't look for me I'm just a story you've been told[00:27.00]So let's pretend a little longer[00:32.00]Cause when we're gone[00:35.00]Everything goes on[00:40.00]Well you were staring at the window[00:45.00]And I said I wanna take you to the sea[00:52.00]And when I'm better we'll do everything[00:57.00]I gotta stop making promises I can't keep[01:03.00]But if I was gone tomorrow[01:06.00]Won't the waves crash on[01:09.00]Is it selfish that I'm happy[01:12.00]As we pass the setting sun[01:15.00]Someday I'll be overcast[01:18.00]But you won't have to cry[01:22.00]Cause we'll do the grieving[01:25.00]While I'm by your side[01:28.00]I said[01:29.00]Don't try to make yourself remember darling[01:35.00]Don't look for me I'm just a story you've been told[01:40.00]So let's pretend a little longer[01:46.00]Cause when we're gone[01:48.00]Everything goes on[02:06.00]And I'm so scared of getting used to this[02:11.00]All the vines that keep you tethered in your room[02:18.00]Well someday both of us are leaving here[02:23.00]But for now I'll just bring the sea to you[02:29.00]Will you meet me in the daylight[02:32.00]Like we did before[02:35.00]Then I felt you on my shoulder[02:38.00]And you weren't suffering anymore[02:41.00]Said I'm sorry that you worried[02:44.00]But don't apologize[02:47.00]I told you to forget me[02:51.00]But you stayed by my side[02:53.00]When I said[02:54.00]Don't try to make yourself remember darling[03:00.00]Don't look for me I'm just a story you've been told[03:06.00]So let's pretend a little longer[03:11.00]And when we're gone[03:17.00]Everything goes on